- Install KLARAPTOR by following the instruction in INSTALL.
- clang should be installed with make install
- NVIDIA cuda must be intalled; the path must be set
	CUDA_PATH
- add CUPTI lib64 path to LD_LIBRARY_PATH
- need gcc 7.4
- CUDA 9.xx
- build_dp_for_kernels.sh is using clang rather than clang-LLVM-version
- you should reload the nvidia module, easiest way is rebooting your os.
- need bash, make, gcc
